creator: Noah  Lee
descriptionHtml:
Can you plan the intensity (or weight) or the strategy for any workout? Most people don't know their workout level (or limit) and hesitate to choose the intensity (or weight) for a workout.

On the other hand, records tell you what your level is. It helps motivate you to continue working hard and prevents injuries from overtraining.

Records are an essential factor in CrossFit and are an essential tool for your growth. If you're enjoying CrossFit, why not start recording now?
descriptionShort: Log your Crossfit WOD, 1RM, and Everything.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fixes
* Fixed sign-in retry error message.
* If you're tired of hitting the back button endlessly, you can now exit the app when you click the back button on the root page.

title: Daily WOD - Log Crossfit WOD

creator: Noah  Lee
descriptionHtml:
Strengthens the connection between box coaches and members, making training more effective.

First, the app's WOD-sharing feature helps facilitate communication between box coaches and members. Through the app, coaches can create their WODs and share them with members. It allows members to set specific, clear workout goals and grow with their coach.

The app makes it easy for members to keep track of their WODs - each member can enter their WOD record and use the data to understand their fitness level. Members can plan more effective workouts and make faster progress.

Members can also see each other's records. It provides even more motivation and allows members to measure and compare their performance.

Finally, it increases collaboration between box coaches and members. Coaches can monitor members' records and provide feedback individually. It allows members to create a more personalized workout plan and work with their coach to improve their performance.

Overall, the app enhances communication and collaboration between box coaches and members, resulting in more effective training.
descriptionShort: Strengthens the connection between coaches and members.
